Class HdbOfficer

java.lang.Object
sc2002.bto.entity.User
sc2002.bto.entity.HdbOfficer
All Implemented Interfaces:
IApplicationProcessing, IEnquiryManagement
public class HdbOfficer extends User implements IEnquiryManagement, IApplicationProcessing
Represents an HDB Officer in the BTO Management System. This class extends the User class and implements IEnquiryManagement and IApplicationProcessing interfaces. HDB Officers assist in processing applications, booking flats, and handling enquiries.
